Basic steps to deploy a cloud infrastructure based on OpenStack using puppet


MANDATORY STEPS:

1. Complete the steps in the installation guide you will find in the installPuppetOpenstackModule directory

2. Complete the steps in the installation guide you will find in the defineOpenstackGeneralConfig directory

OPTIONAL STEPS depends on your goals

- If you wanto to deploy all Openstack Services over one single node follow the installation guide in the 
  installAllInOneNode directory
- If you wanto to deploy all Openstack Compute Servive follow the installation guide in the installComputeNode 
  directory
